window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dangerous Affair is a one-night-stand-turned-friends to lovers, age gap, alpha protector romantic suspense novel with a tortured hero and a take-no-sh!t heroine who has a feisty, opinionated grandmother who likes to butt into other people's relationships.</b></p> <p>It was supposed to be a fantasy-fueled, one-night stand, something to make me shed my good girl inhibitions. Imagine my shock when the sexy stranger I spent the night with showed up the next morning at a breakfast my grandmother was hosting.</p> <p>When he took me back to my hotel, one night turned into a weekend. That was where it was supposed to end. I flew back to Las Vegas, thinking I'd never see the emotionally unavailable Wilson McCray again.</p> <p>He had other plans.</p> <p>Atlee Levine wasn't supposed to get under my skin.</p> <p>I'd already failed one woman. I'd dedicated my life to my career—it was safer that way. I had no business falling in love with the strong-willed, beautiful woman.</p> <p>When I found out she was tangled up with the man I'd been hired to take down, I realized I'd break every rule to protect her. I kept her safe until my guilt crashed around me. A few words in anger sent Atlee running straight into the hands of the enemy.</p> <p>Takeback has saved hundreds of trafficking victims—will they make it in time to save the woman Wilson's fallen in love with or will they be too late? And if she's rescued, can Wilson do what needs to be done to win her back or will his past continue to rule his future?</p> <p><b>Caution in this book you'll find a bossy alpha hero who's a whole lot damaged and a heroine who will fight for her man.</b></p>"; 
